{"tid":1585502,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企有牛蜱應該點做","createTime":"2019-09-21T15:34:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T15:15:26.000Z","uid":55623,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"23b2013b91c1ac1d2681f4ea0fd46f55ee16412f","tid":1585502,"uid":55623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:34:27.000Z","msg":"我執咗隻狗仔返屋企<br />\n然後佢有勁多牛蜱 滴左藥之後啲牛蜱唔見哂<br />\n但依家發現屋企地下有好多牛蜱bb<br />\n連床都有屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日帶左佢再去沖涼杜蝨<br />\n但屋企個啲我應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買滅蝨彈有無用 同埋電器會唔會炸壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5cae6945ec00ee8767cb6ed483db923e8d40471","tid":1585502,"uid":55623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:35:26.000Z","msg":"諗到成屋蟲就好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c13ae72da6cbe681393b5a56adc17d40c9fa16","tid":1585502,"uid":136539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"23b2013b91c1ac1d2681f4ea0fd46f55ee16412f","tid":1585502,"uid":55623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:34:27.000Z","msg":"我執咗隻狗仔返屋企<br />\n然後佢有勁多牛蜱 滴左藥之後啲牛蜱唔見哂<br />\n但依家發現屋企地下有好多牛蜱bb<br />\n連床都有屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日帶左佢再去沖涼杜蝨<br />\n但屋企個啲我應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買滅蝨彈有無用 同埋電器會唔會炸壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:48:26.000Z","msg":"試過成屋都係 要搵日帶狗狗出街 收埋d植物 買個d家居炸彈 炸完之後會見到死曬係地下 之後全屋用水抹一次 先好帶翻狗狗翻屋企 因為會lam死佢嫁 炸過一次 無曬"},{"pid":"18f28b4c7c2670dee700983303fde3db39bd9ca5","tid":1585502,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:50:26.000Z","msg":"帶埋隻狗去驗血 <br />\n中左牛蜱熱就麻煩"},{"pid":"de70b20471cc83e3d468031522cb2d781d169e08","tid":1585502,"uid":194203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T21:13:31.000Z","msg":"試過狗仔身上有牛蜱<br />\n如果再見到可以用消毒藥水焗暈佢 之後先禁死or沖走佢<br />\n另外要留意下狗仔會唔會無乜精神牙肉紅腫<br />\n怕佢有牛蜱熱<br />\n最後記得買個不蚤鈴或者tickless比狗狗帶住<br />\n個人覺得有效"},{"pid":"8b2c114eb054664f1dad7bd619814a4616751688","tid":1585502,"uid":307725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T21:17:45.000Z","msg":"去惠康買支biokill噴下周圍"},{"pid":"151104cbbdd5f8d5b8dd0dfe53b4b393441b57fc","tid":1585502,"uid":7860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T21:57:59.000Z","msg":"大隻果D唔好禁爆佢 會爆BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bff59aba36314659cea202b724639d6915b6ddc","tid":1585502,"uid":191036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:55:46.000Z","msg":"與蟲同眠左幾個月好有心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我早幾年都瀨過野搞到成屋都係, 兩隻中型狗成身都有, 牛蜱成蟲灰灰地色脹卜卜, 果陣唔知咩黎整爆佢好多水, 後尾先知啲&quot;水&quot;原來係幼蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n炸彈一個禮拜炸一次炸過兩三次都仲係有好多牛蜱啲屋, 最後滴frontline plus搞掂左, 我係正常用法每月一次, 滴完身上啲蟲開始少左(我估係滴完啲血有毒毒Q死), 屋入邊啲蟲就見一隻捉一隻, 由發現成屋蟲開始計前前後後清左大約三個月先唔再見到有活體<br />\n啲牛蜱好鐘意向上爬爬到件野最頂頂個尖端, 試下用A4紙自制啲尖尖地既錐體, 佢地一爬上去就好易見到, 捉到就用酒精浸死佢以絕後患<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a23e3cfd5781d9788080aef0e2cef81deb469f8","tid":1585502,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZNd41Gu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http